{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1689-03a_015","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Sur les Conquestes de Monseigneur le Dauphin. Ode","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure Galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mars, première partie [tome 3], 1689, p. 15-22.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},{"#1":{"value":"Vous voulez bien qu’aprés vous avoir parlé d’un jeune Prince, heureux d’avoir trouvé retraite auprés d’un grand Roy, je vous parle d’un autre encore plus heureux de l’avoir pour Pere. C’est de Monseigneur le Dauphin. Je n’ay pu depuis quatre mois vous faire part de tous les Vers que l’on a faits à sa gloire, parce que j’en avois assez pour remplir toutes mes Lettres ; ainsi j’ay cru vous en devoir donner moins à la fois, &amp; vous en envoyer plus souvent. En voicy de M","id":"/div/p[1]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p[1]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Magnin, de l’Academie Royale d’Arles. Cet illustre Auteur a souvent remporté des Prix, &amp; merité les éloges que vous luy avez donnez.","id":"/div/p[1]/#2"}}],"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"SUR","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"LES CONQUESTES","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"DE","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[4]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"MONSEIGNEUR","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[6]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"LE DAUPHIN.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[8]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"ODE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[10]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Autrefois lors que la Gloire","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Me demandoit quelques Vers,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’allois, Filles de Memoire,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Consulter vos chants divers.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je voyois par mille exemples","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que tout couroit à vos Temples","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Implorer quelque secours ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais je vous le dis sans feindre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Non, vous ne sçauriez atteindre","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A la carriere où je cours.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je ne sçay si je m’égare,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais dans mon vol sans pareil,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si j’ay le destin d’Icare,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je vais plus prés du Soleil.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’apperçois l’Aigle timide","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la hauteur où me guide","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’ardeur dont je suis épris ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ses foibles aisles s’abaissent,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ses regards me paroissent","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Epouvantez &amp; surpris.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" C’est la conqueste étonnante","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De tout le Palatinat,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui sans doute l’épouvante,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et fait que le cœur luy bat.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La lâcheté de Bisance","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ayant enflé sa puissance,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle ne s’attendoit pas","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’avoir en cherchant querelle","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par une audace nouvelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Deux Grands LOUIS sur les bras.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle croyoit, affermie","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par quelques exploits guerriers,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Trouver la France endormie","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A l’ombre de ses Lauriers ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais on ne peut la surprendre,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Philisbourg vient de l’apprendre","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En dépit de ses marais,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et l’Europe en ces alarmes","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pourra juger si nos armes","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’enroüillent pendant la Paix.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le Heros dont la vaillance","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A cimenté son repos,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La met par sa vigilance","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A couvert de ses Rivaux ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et formé par sa sagesse","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Dauphin qui s’interesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qui s’expose pour nous,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par sa premiere conqueste,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fait déja tourner la teste","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A nos superbes Jaloux.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Peut-estre l’ont-ils pû croire,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que ce Dauphin genereux","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voudroit toujours de sa gloire","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Goûter le repos heureux ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le Grand Loüis luy-mesme","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont la sagesse est extrême,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Craindroit de le hazarder ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais voicy comme il raisonne,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[17]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’il veut porter la Couronne,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il apprenne à la garder.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qu’il aille sur la frontiere","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où l’on ne le connoist pas,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Montrer de quelle maniere","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il défendra ses Etats.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est vray que de la France","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’ay redoublé la puissance","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par mille exploits glorieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais la grandeur de courage,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que je luy laisse en partage","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vaut encor mille fois mieux.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" A ces mots pour se resoudre","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Perdit-il un seul moment ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Aigle qui porte la foudre","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fend les airs moins brusquement.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A peine il part de Versailles,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’on apprend que les murailles","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont fait bréche à Philisbourg.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout se rend, les Places fortes","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ouvrent à l’envy les portes,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et le voilà de retour.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Tandis que la Renommée","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par des recits étonnans","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Conte à l’Europe alarmée","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tous ces exploits surprenans,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"LOUIS prepare des Festes","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour honorer les Conquestes","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du Heros qu’il a formé.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il l’embrasse, il le carresse,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de sa tendre jeunesse","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voit tout le monde charmé.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Cent fois plus heureux qu’Auguste,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que Trajan, que Constantin,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Faveur rare, mais tres-juste,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il renaist dans son Dauphin.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’il monte dans sa carriere,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de son char de lumiere","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’il luy cede le Timon,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son coup d’essay nous enseigne","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il ne faut pas que l’on craigne","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La cheute de Phaëton.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}}]}}}